1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,820
A man who did not know his place,
he presumed to ask me questions.

2
00:00:05,140 --> 00:00:07,980
We do a lot of presuming here in
the United States, Consul General.

3
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:09,380
It comes with the turf.

4
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:12,780
You fuck young boys, Valdez.

5
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:14,000
Are you a madman?

